 Manzanita, Oregon 
 Welcome To Manzanita! 
 Neahkahnie Mountain 
 Nestled in the protective shadow of Neahkahnie Mountain, Manzanita is the perfect year round beach vacation. Experience the best of what we have to offer: fishing on the Nehalem River, camping at Nehalem Bay State Park, wine tasting, shopping at quaint boutiques, and